{"tid":1951123,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"謝霆鋒擺花街舖劈租近半 7.3萬租出","createTime":"2020-03-30T19:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T06:34:14.000Z","uid":185631,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3232d1bf8844c532961cc382835eb4a2b2d294","tid":1951123,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"零售市道一片死寂，部份名人旗下舖位都要減價租出。市場消息稱，藝人謝霆鋒持有的擺花街26號地下，面積約700方呎，連約500方呎閣樓，由2018年底丟吉至今近1年半，一直叫租13.8萬元，新近終以約7.3萬元租出，較叫租低47％，若以2012年購入1.17億元計，回報僅不足1厘。參考差估署最新資料，該舖2020/21年度最新租值為123.6萬元，按年度減10%，平均每月即約10.3萬元，今次租出價比其租值低近三成。"},{"pid":"a29bb55f9e0864015d1c92c6f7e7c97d483d3a23","tid":1951123,"uid":156363,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T22:13:25.000Z","msg":"佢早幾年搵咁多人仔，根本唔志在呢收租呢啲細數目啦。"},{"pid":"f0959c1824baf418c3493e00ad99c01c99466115","tid":1951123,"uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T22:19:43.000Z","msg":"丟空左年半都唔減<br />\n而家市差先租出"},{"pid":"13850e76a37c17d0979341db185d303c3088370a","tid":1951123,"uid":126317,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T23:05:17.000Z","msg":"應該租比陳冠x 做炮房"},{"pid":"4f3d0907d7b72bbddbc9339a0134d6abe582e994","tid":1951123,"uid":68001,"like":10,"dislike":15,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"13850e76a37c17d0979341db185d303c3088370a","tid":1951123,"uid":126317,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T23:05:17.000Z","msg":"應該租比陳冠x 做炮房"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T23:16:06.000Z","msg":"戇撚尻，垃圾回覆，九唔搭八"},{"pid":"38bbf15cae509526cce45a00849f05c79cd90c85","tid":1951123,"uid":1348,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T23:21:08.000Z","msg":"樓上謝檸檬本人?"},{"pid":"69c8d095a5934c6ed8a6f81b24c2e935ed61bff9","tid":1951123,"uid":53844,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"4f3d0907d7b72bbddbc9339a0134d6abe582e994","tid":1951123,"uid":68001,"like":10,"dislike":15,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"13850e76a37c17d0979341db185d303c3088370a","tid":1951123